  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<img src=\"Art%20-%20Items/artifacts/crown_of_sunlight_floats_like_a_halo_above_.webp\" /><p><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X, 'Font Awesome 5 Free'\">A plain silver circlet. On the outer-facing ring in beautiful Taldane calligraphy:<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:ALBR55X, 'Font Awesome 5 Free';font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:ALBR55X, 'Font Awesome 5 Free';font-size:13px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\">Where loss and love intertwine<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\" />True enlightenment we find.<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\" /><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\" /></em>On the inner ring, scratched in a crude scrawl with a sharp blade after the item had seen years of use:<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:ALBR55X, 'Font Awesome 5 Free';font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:ALBR55X, 'Font Awesome 5 Free';font-size:13px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\">I will never get over you.</em></span></p><p></p><p>This plain looking silver circlet radiates no magic or alignment auras until it is placed upon the head of a good-aligned positive channeler.</p><p>It then begins to glow and floats off their head, expanding into a bright ring of light that floats like a halo. While in this form, it bolsters positive channels by +2d6, and allows a new type of hybrid-channel.</p><p>Hybrid Channels both heal, at -1 dice of the channelers normal amount, and harm undead also at -1 dice of the channelers normal. This function costs 2 uses of the wearers channeling for that day.</p><p>All the wearers light spells see their durations extended, as the metamagic effect.</p><p>The circlet also functions as a cloak of resistance +4, adds +4 to the TouchAC of the wearer, and is a +2 wisdom +2 charisma enhancement item.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p>",
      "instructions": "",
      "unidentified": "<p>A plain silver circlet. On the outer-facing ring in beautiful Taldane calligraphy:<br /><em>Where loss and love intertwine<br />True enlightenment we find.<br /><br /></em><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X, 'Font Awesome 5 Free'\">On the inner ring, scratched in a crude scrawl with a sharp blade after the item had seen years of use:</span><br /><em>I will never get over you.</em></p>"
    },
